Package javax.jaxtx.model.btp

Interface Summary
Atom The Atom extension of the basic UserTransaction interface.
Cohesion A Cohesion extension of the basic UserTransaction.
Qualifier A qualifier for the core transaction engine to use.
StatusItem An instance of this interface is created for each inferior when its status is required.
Vote All votes from prepare are instances of this interface.
VoteCancel The inferior votes that it has cancelled.
VoteConfirm The inferior votes to confirm.
VoteResign The inferior votes that all of its inferiors have resigned from the transaction.
 

Class Summary
PreparedStatus The inferior has prepared.
PreparingStatus The inferior is in the process of preparing.
ResignedStatus The inferior has resigned from the transaction.
ResigningStatus The inferior is in the process of resigning from the transaction.
 

Exception Summary
HazardException A heuristic hazard has occurred: some participants confirmed, some cancelled and some we just don't know!
MixedException A heuristic mixed has occurred: some participants confirmed and some cancelled.
TransactionCancelledException The transaction (atom or cohesion) cancelled when it was instructed to confirm.
TransactionConfirmedException The transaction (atom or cohesion) cancelled when it was instructed to confirm.
